    <item>
      <title>Sheikah Techniques</title>
      <author>Catzy123</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/450989</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/450989#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">2e0f3f8bdf147de4f128155e989c74fe4277b935</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Nov 2025 20:08:58 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671cee17c1abd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/650d7f1c3d8b8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671ced9090a8c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64c1c57e59163.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671cee0bd23e1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64905a819edec.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64a7bc954515e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671cedbc70335.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/650bbe562d85b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671ced1740722.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671ced4390208.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Compatability with small addition&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Optimization&lt;/em&gt;: Works with Tkmm v2.0.0-rc1 now&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added different no-shield guarding&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/tQTX8sq.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I have always mained Sheik in Smash Ultimate, and now part of her moveset and Impa’s are in TOTK because Link decided to get Sheikah training in the time between BOTW and TOTK so that he can utilize his own abilities more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;(This is my first mod I made.)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;All animations were made by myself. Flurry Rush ones are from Smash.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;I also highly recommend playing it with any difficulty mod that makes the game more challenging.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Creating Videos with this mod is also completely allowed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;And checking out the Installation tab is really important.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;This mod only replaces animations but also changes some stuff like:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Remove Lag from almost every animation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Hitboxes from Katana Charge attack and Slash Attacks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Running Speed is increased&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Enables to activate Bullet Time when jumping while running on flat ground. (when not selecting slow run)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Always Silent&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Double Jump&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/mQPAkhA.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Added Compatability for Tkmm&amp;nbsp;v2.0.0-rc1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link learned to parry better with swords while having no shield equipped (still needs some work but its there)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/parry.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Any support is really appreciated&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/PwVTpiG.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;He learned the Impa/Naruto run to move faster and jumps Differently&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/run_and_jump.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;Alternate&lt;/font&gt; Run option.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Also the way the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Yiga ability works is different&lt;/span&gt;, in general its more usefull&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/second_run_and_yiga.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link attacks differently and flurry rush is even faster.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/fast_flurry_and_normal_attack.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link has a&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;different stance&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;while he also learned how to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;wield a spear&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;differently and also learning how to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;teleport differently and faster&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(loading screen was cut out)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/pose_and_tp_with_staff.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Changed some camera poses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/camera.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;falls differently&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;too&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/fall.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Added ASB edits&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;These changes wont be mergeable&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;with other ASB files, unless i make a compatability patch, which i will try to do soon, most big overhaul mods edit ASB but its not that important of a file)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Changes: Swim Dash is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;faster&lt;/span&gt;, side hopping lag is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;way faster&lt;/span&gt;, earthwake tech is slower (but more useful), he closes his eyes a bit more often in some handsign animations and also does the changes for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;slower run&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;if you chose that as a option, also Spin attack speed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;He has learned to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;roll&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;after landing on the ground, and a real double jump.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br&gt;Double jump can be activated by pressing &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Y&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt; while in the air, but you need to have a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;weapon equipped.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;It can be used &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;multiple times&lt;/span&gt; while in the air, but you can quickly get the double jump back by opening the glider and closing it (&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;old double jump is also still there&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;br&gt;And you&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; cant&lt;/span&gt; draw your bow or fuse while being in the double jump animation,&lt;br&gt;so you will need to draw your bow, a second beforehand&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;(You can still&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; jump attack&lt;/span&gt; while gliding)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/wca1iin.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Relocated Sheath&lt;/span&gt; (Only swords for now) there is also a&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; standalone&lt;/span&gt; pack and replaced a pose with it (Standalone weapons dont get relocated)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Standalone Swords get Reloacated in a scuffed way&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;and 2H/Spear Sheaths are invisible&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/yUE10rDXUuMqldyH5T/giphy.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Ascend&lt;/span&gt; is also&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; Better&lt;/span&gt;, Because of what he learned he doesnt have a "i can't ascend here" animation anymore and he is able to exit it way quicker&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Fuse&lt;/span&gt; and&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; Recal&lt;/span&gt;l and&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; UltaHand&lt;/span&gt; also look different&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Added&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; Sheikah Cloth&lt;/span&gt;, Link is More &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Agile&lt;/span&gt; now by &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Creating a Cloth&lt;/span&gt; with a Technique and he will always &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;throw it away &lt;/span&gt;so that it turns back into thin &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Air&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Can do Insane Stunts with Tulin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;(For now there is only&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; this Fabric&lt;/span&gt; and a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Yiga fabric&lt;/span&gt; that was replaced against &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;CeCe fabrik&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/mnOyr4MFpAdX9cWlNf/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/MWHyb2mfQlcvYBX8Ji/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;THE &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;FORBIDDEN SHEIKAH TECHNIQUE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;del&gt;&lt;i&gt;totk glitch enhanced by my mod&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/del&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/zlq3NwFNp9nJKl315Y/giphy.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Wallrun and Quick Climb/Slide&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;but you cant "Climb" Diagonal anymore&lt;/span&gt; (because it was buggy and link went flying)&lt;br&gt;Use &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Speed Elixier&lt;/span&gt; to Wallrun Faster&lt;br&gt;Left is Normal, Right is with Elixier&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/nulgE9sgcnKZvaHpNH/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/eQvEuNjsAxjAx2sU5Y/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Changed &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Equip Animation&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;2H Charge Attack&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Gave it a Different stance&lt;/span&gt; and&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; Different Jump&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Slash&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;b&gt;The Jump Slash is now able to Multihit, Very Effective against Big enemies&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;br&gt;(Equip Animation gets played faster when Speed Elexier is On)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/duRCnLxgxHljLWDq8f/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/dWJDLboEJUaEVbKHEZ/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/FuguF3lRh2XR20pZ5t/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link has learned a way to get out of &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Ragdoll&lt;/span&gt; Quicker&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/mJTDZjPoASTonPKyV6/giphy.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Added More &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Camera Poses&lt;/span&gt; and Replaced &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Crouch&lt;/span&gt; with one. (Two of them are poses from &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Offical art&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;(&lt;b&gt;Unequip or Requip Shield for the 2 Sword poses&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/cRNrwoqHIzXtFvDiZu/giphy.gif" width="35%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/AH4k0cwbun7eUDbwY1/giphy.gif" width="25%"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/QKgcAOsqg6wIrrhFVl/giphy.gif" width="45%"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/tL2CI6OkqJinHQBcM4/giphy.gif" width="35%"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/Cmxu6KnbCuWlcw88Ym/giphy.gif" width="35%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sword &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Equip&lt;/span&gt; Animation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/0I6NlQF7FTyDkczys8/giphy.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link Holds his Sword &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Upside Down&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/TbHEn9pEEBpWBLcW4J/giphy-downsized-large.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Changed the Jump Animation while Shield Surfing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Removed&lt;/span&gt; Sword Side Step (Because it Happens Always on Accident)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Double Jump&lt;/span&gt;. Shield Jump and and go out of Shield Jump instantly afterwards.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;You can Upgrade&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;the Double Jump&lt;/span&gt; by Fusing a Wing Glider to your Shield&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/ma7sutRK42O97KNUwm/giphy.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Removed Lag From &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Almost all animations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Examples: Dash attack, Charge Attacks, Throwing Materials, Converting from Jumping into Running, Backflips, Flurry Rushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/w1cKIc5x5qaUnrbO3u/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/B0wYllIVPMbkCeKiJc/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Replaced Falling Animation with Diving Animation&lt;/span&gt; and replaced the Animation for Jumping while Shield Surfing against Shield Jump Animation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link has learned to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Charge his Attacks while running&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and he replaced the right spin attack with the left spin attack (cause it looks cooler)(From Hyrule warriors Link Charge Attack)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/SdjTfS48NB2YiTprPF/giphy.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExbmY1NXE5MHJkeGp3NHd4emc1N3Bxbjh0eXZ6em5kdXkweGlzMjkzaSZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/aKOoJtnz9BW8synXdg/giphy-downsized-large.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Has learned to use 2H weapons quicker and more efficent&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/tAJOP1aaZiLD9VG4fq/giphy.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sword Slash attack Replaced with Sheik Down air from smash ult&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Onehanded/Twohandedsword Sneakstrike and Katana Charge Attack replaced with&amp;nbsp;Iaijutsu Technique&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExZjg4ajV6eTg5M3dlN3VrbjFyMHBiYzV2cTRtemFiZGZ6eWlza2dmOSZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/epBdnPIej4LCwhShdC/giphy-downsized-large.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;img src="https://imgur.com/WrdfJ1w.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;The only Version that&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;isnt&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;supported is 1.0.0, because its buggy, but Tkmm might make it work&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you want to play with&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;OTHER MODS&lt;/span&gt; OR want to use ONLY &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;SPECIFIC ANIMATIONS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;you will need to use &lt;a href="https://totkmods.github.io/tkmm/downloads/" target="_blank"&gt;TKMM&lt;/a&gt; its simple to use, you just add the Tkcl file from the download from this mod to TKMM, the tkcl file has all the options and lets you decide the options inside TKMM, its also the most recommended way to install this mod&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you just want to play the mod with everything and without any other mods&lt;/b&gt;, here is how:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Ryujinx:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Open the zip file, then right click totk and place the file in Mod Data Location&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Yuzu&lt;/span&gt;: Open the zip file and then right click totk and place the file in Mod Data Location&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Switch&lt;/span&gt;: Open the zip and search the "romfs" folder and place it in "atmosphere\content\0100F2C0115B6000" on your sdcard&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Mod also Pairs Really Well with the Autobuild &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/466003"&gt;Ninjutsu Mod&lt;/a&gt;, you should really Check it out.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;if you have problems installing it, you add me on Discord "catzy3979"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;In General it just makes you look Cooler and makes Combat stuff look more intense and smoother, have fun&lt;br&gt;</description>
