      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Nov 2025 08:08:32 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67cc4e55277b2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d68e82b9c4e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d68e83075fe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67de851ae563f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67e91887e2f8c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67e9185cc3513.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67cc9528243e4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fb60beabd6e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fb60be6a477.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67cc952806018.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fb60bed22c0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d68edfa473e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67dc1e5ac3e1c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67cc95283f21d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67cc952802b0d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67cc4ef8c0728.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67cc4ef926e41.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; NudeLink V2.0.2&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Compatibility with Tkmm v2.0.0-rc1 has been added.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;This mod is a Totk port of &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/487958"&gt;NudeLink V2.0.1&lt;/a&gt; created for Wii-U Botw.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Game version only supports 1.2.1&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Differences from the BotW version -&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Removed non-existent armor in Totk.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;New edit of Totk armor.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Removed or reworked armor that did not have the appropriate physical properties.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;This mod requires &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tools/17165"&gt;Tkmm&lt;/a&gt;, so please install it beforehand. For each armor, enable the ones you need from the Options tab.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you find any bugs, please report them in the comments section. (I may not be able to fix all of them...)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There are 4 tkcl files packed in one zip folder, please choose and install the version you like, such as hairless or no acc.</description>
